{"tid":965003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西安特色主題酒店嚇親人　床尾廁所都有兵馬俑守住","createTime":"2019-01-01T17:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T11:59:16.000Z","uid":66271,"like":182,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb9a10b85d158a188118def9e55539fcd0acc07","tid":965003,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2257614/org/a5da3572fb6f537bd87e0294163fc57b.jpg/v5eEKBWfFbxBxLUjwApR6TqTTg_dK6cJxW75Q8Vu-UM?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2257614%2Forg%2Fa5da3572fb6f537bd87e0294163fc57b.jpg%2Fv5eEKBWfFbxBxLUjwApR6TqTTg_dK6cJxW75Q8Vu-UM%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=558acc70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以秦始皇兵馬俑為主題的酒店你有夠膽入住嗎？近日內地有blogger入住西安一間兵馬俑主題酒店，房間內的佈置令人不寒而慄，無論睡房、廁所、廚房，牆身都嵌入兵馬俑，住客睡覺洗澡甚至上廁所時，感覺都被兵馬俑盯着，詭異的眼神教人完全不敢直視，就連拍片的blogger亦表示自己因此徹夜未眠。不少網民看片後都表示太驚嚇：「誰會敢住？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254502/org/1137096448459297fa3d4436d1fe94cb.JPG/ci0VNr-4EWFBPjlEex6VxEVGneAaeoXv0RT8UtEU_FI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254502%2Forg%2F1137096448459297fa3d4436d1fe94cb.JPG%2Fci0VNr-4EWFBPjlEex6VxEVGneAaeoXv0RT8UtEU_FI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c4518c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地著名blogger「畢導THU」畢嘯天早前於微博上載片段，表示上星期到了西安，他稱朋友為他預訂酒店休息，於是到埗後即登記入住。沒想到一打開房門，惡夢就來了。<br />\n<br />\n他於片中逐一介紹套房的設施，可見不論睡床的床頭、床尾、坐廁前、甚至客廳，每幅牆都嵌入至少3個高矮不一的兵馬俑，連床下都整齊地排列着兵馬俑。即使自己吃飯、睡覺、去廁所都避不開兵馬俑詭異的目光，恐怖感瞬間激增。<br />\n<br />\n畢嘯天解釋，因為房中實在有太多兵馬俑，即使至凌晨他都不敢睡覺。片中見他兩度嘗試入睡但也失敗，最後他還需要播放相聲片段，令房中的氣氛變得熱鬧，惟他最後徹夜未眠，非常可憐。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都直言酒店佈置太詭異，「可以說是非常的身臨其境」、「讓自己體驗做秦始皇的感覺」、「不吉利吧，再怎麼說也是墓葬品」，有網民更笑言：「你睡不着是因為你沒有關燈，一關燈兵馬俑就變活了」、「睡不着可以讓兵馬俑給講睡前故事啊」。畢嘯天後來在微博表示，「兵馬俑酒店」成為了近期微博熱搜榜字詞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254529/org/d11ae910d6d5be6708a1b7cbeed01edb.JPG/Ovebq4h40yUCffCBOt8hTW0ySln9K0mMGmDXVBpg11Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254529%2Forg%2Fd11ae910d6d5be6708a1b7cbeed01edb.JPG%2FOvebq4h40yUCffCBOt8hTW0ySln9K0mMGmDXVBpg11Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=80978041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據旅遊預訂網站「攜程」（Ctrip）的資料顯示，該酒店名叫「西安兵馬俑自助公寓」，若要租住單人房一晚，價格為269人民幣（約305港元）；如要租住套房（一廳一房連洗手間），一晚價格為358人民幣（約407港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254531/org/ef82fb36423961bf421141f4b654c089.JPG/RPkZXWmeODQ3mO2QGaHpvSYqdyIyliznX2PNe19jzXs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254531%2Forg%2Fef82fb36423961bf421141f4b654c089.JPG%2FRPkZXWmeODQ3mO2QGaHpvSYqdyIyliznX2PNe19jzXs&h=06d4ecb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254530/org/083561210e1a738a40a0131ee147d553.JPG/MjM_Xr04bbLZz9fvA5gQpu0MC2HFI0iwLroPpC66D6Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254530%2Forg%2F083561210e1a738a40a0131ee147d553.JPG%2FMjM_Xr04bbLZz9fvA5gQpu0MC2HFI0iwLroPpC66D6Q&h=0179f65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254526/org/e7876d15b5947066ec2f896ebf405a46.JPG/GxlzeueJYX9KVzf_amXunNBf5N-OI_2WcZ-b33Gfm98\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254526%2Forg%2Fe7876d15b5947066ec2f896ebf405a46.JPG%2FGxlzeueJYX9KVzf_amXunNBf5N-OI_2WcZ-b33Gfm98&h=b34a360e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254532/org/aa32e29858a5bb0572c90f356bbc1868.JPG/_a3xO6BzRa2bvRtqHCFvdL9NjcSMKIrY0iuhStIroUo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2254532%2Forg%2Faa32e29858a5bb0572c90f356bbc1868.JPG%2F_a3xO6BzRa2bvRtqHCFvdL9NjcSMKIrY0iuhStIroUo&h=1ef8b9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2254527/org/fb874463145d868bc3f81c72adc63ee4.JPG/5B8